		<h4>You really think this is "Like fantasy football, but better"?</h4>
		<p>Yes. As a fan, it is better to root for the Bears to win than for Adrian Peterson to score. Sharp League has the fun and competition of fantasy football, without the funky distortions in viewing experience.</p>
