		<h4>What's the history behind this?</h4>
		<p>We've been around since 2010, learning and improving with each iteration. Some of our best features&mdash;such as live update and "hidden" bets&mdash;are a direct result of user feedback.
		We try our hardest to keep our users happy.</p>
